<hr />
<p>We as Staff would like to thank everyone who took the time to participate in the Annual SCP Foundation Community Survey! The number of responses was heartwarming and to see we have such an involved and active community-base is wonderful. We had a total of 5,456 unique responses this year, which is fantastic. The amount of feedback we received will allow us to grow and improve the site as we progress into the future. Thank you to all who participated.</p>
